      "message": "I further made a small modification: Entries are erased from fruWriteCtxMap on atEnd completion. Timer callback paths release only the data buffer because they execute inside sdbusplus::Timer::timeoutHandler(), which continues to access eventSource after the user callback returns.",
      "parentUuid": "018d8ca4_2156a20e",
